flowRoot.flowPara: (1) Direct invocation of send to immediately display comment
外部直接调用send来立即显示弹幕
(2) Comments managed by CM.timeline are sent or skipped based on playhead time.
If the playhead was fast forwarded or reversed no comments will be sent.
每次播放时间更新时，时间轴会派发上次更新的播放时间和目前播放器时间期间内的弹幕。
时间跨度太大（快进）或者新时间更早（回看）时则不会派发弹幕。
